# `=+ "tislus"`

`[%tsls p=hoon q=hoon]`: combine a new noun with the subject.

## Expands to

```
=>([p .] q)
```

## Syntax

Regular: _2-fixed_.

## Discussion

`=+` ("tislus") is the simplest way of "declaring a variable."

## Examples

```
~zod:dojo> =foo  |=  a=@
                 =+  b=1
                 =+  c=2
                 :(add a b c)
~zod:dojo> (foo 5)
8
```

